Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.96,0:01:18.87,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}You changed me so much I don't remember what I was like before we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.27,0:01:23.36,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}The breeze caresses our cheeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.36,0:01:25.47,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}Lullaby of Birdland...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.72,0:01:29.69,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}As we run down the slope,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.04,0:01:33.75,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}our flimsy shadows extend.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.75,0:01:38.69,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}It's like a neverending summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.69,0:01:44.20,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}It feels like when we snuck into the pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.48,0:01:50.23,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}Yeah, let's swim with our clothes on. Jump in!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.58,0:01:52.92,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}It's an intense spiral of temptation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.35,0:01:57.44,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}A beat pierces my heart. A strange one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.93,0:02:01.01,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}It vanishes after a quick spark.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.13,0:02:03.81,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}Even on bad days, I dress up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.06,0:02:08.80,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}and dance to some swing. The music quickly surrounds me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.80,0:02:11.65,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}What is this dance exactly? I can't stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.65,0:02:20.91,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}Don't leave me. It's stuck in my head, and I can't get it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.31,0:02:24.00,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}The melody...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.76,0:02:29.79,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}is like love.
