Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.07,0:00:36.26,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.26,0:00:37.51,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Nothin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.02,0:00:45.10,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't used to being in a different class than his friends
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.10,0:00:47.29,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,This is his first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.16,0:00:56.91,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Um, you've got a petal in your hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.91,0:00:58.57,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay. I'll get it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.77,0:02:45.01,apollon main,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,Nishimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.28,0:02:48.02,apollon main,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy we're in the same class again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.02,0:02:48.95,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.95,0:02:50.67,apollon main,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.68,0:02:52.65,apollon main,,0000,0000,0000,,We just did our self introductions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.53,0:02:54.36,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.01,0:02:59.26,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You got his ticket for the sleeper car too, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.26,0:03:01.10,apollon main,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.10,0:03:03.07,apollon main,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,He said to keep it a secret from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.65,0:03:06.70,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Because of that, I had a nice trip. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.23,0:03:12.04,apollon main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally over!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.04,0:03:15.34,apollon main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,We should've decided the class rep by drawing lots in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:16.71,apollon main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,No kiddin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.95,0:03:19.59,apollon main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I heard there was already a fight in class 10!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.64,0:03:22.94,apollon main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just glad I wasn't put in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.55,0:03:33.10,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you done already, boxing club?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.68,0:03:36.30,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd have a little more spirit than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.30,0:03:37.80,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.80,0:03:39.47,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.47,0:03:41.08,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me "Hi"!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.08,0:03:44.70,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you fighting on the first day of school?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.70,0:03:47.24,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Just gettin' a little exercise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.18,0:03:51.07,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,That was fun. Been too long since I had a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.07,0:03:52.58,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sen! Are you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.97,0:03:53.87,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.33,0:03:55.68,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.69,0:04:08.72,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.09,0:04:11.00,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.00,0:04:11.56,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.08,0:04:14.43,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You're going over there with that banged-up face?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.36,0:04:16.56,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Is it that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.56,0:04:17.76,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ri.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.41,0:04:22.49,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but would you take this guy to the nurse's office and patch him up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:25.99,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,All right, get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.29,0:04:28.88,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ri, he's in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.88,0:04:29.74,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.66,0:04:35.25,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It still hurts a little,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.87,0:04:37.96,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,but I should get used to it eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.06,0:04:43.29,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,The pain will go away and I'll be able to relax and smile again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.81,0:04:50.67,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to submit this painting to this year's public exhibition.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.67,0:04:53.18,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,This is the one Sentaro modeled for.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.97,0:04:57.27,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.27,0:04:58.74,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.74,0:05:01.42,apollon main,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to force yourself to give me feedback.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.42,0:05:05.20,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry. I don't know much about art.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.20,0:05:08.70,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? That's a strange thing for you to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.84,0:05:13.70,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,After all, painting and jazz are relatively close cousins, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.04,0:05:17.57,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,A painting is created on a space called the canvas,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.57,0:05:20.00,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,while jazz is created during a time called the performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:24.72,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,It's like etching your living self into that place and time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.69,0:05:28.50,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Or something like that.\NI was only repeating someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.50,0:05:32.39,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Junichi was talking about that \Nwhen I went down to the basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.52,0:05:34.81,apollon main,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)\c&H010209&\shad0\bord0\fs30\blur0.75\fnOld newspaper font\b0\frz41.041\pos(586,307)}Fukahori Yurika
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.52,0:05:34.81,apollon main,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)\c&H010209&\shad0\bord0\fs30\blur0.75\fnOld newspaper font\b0\frz71.121\clip(m 1011 419 l 969 396 891 580 980 590)\pos(967,477)}Fukahori Yurika
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.52,0:05:34.81,apollon main,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)\c&H010209&\shad0\bord0\fs30\blur0.75\fnOld newspaper font\b0\pos(830,448)\frz62.54\clip(m 865 389 l 770 472 753 530 824 546)}Fukahori Yurika
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.40,0:05:38.39,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,It's very interesting to listen to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.01,0:05:41.16,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to talk to him more about all kinds of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.61,0:05:47.36,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I went to Tokyo during spring break.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.36,0:05:52.17,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I dropped by his boarding house, but he wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.17,0:05:53.91,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.91,0:05:56.45,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, he hadn't been back for a long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.45,0:05:59.42,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,so there were a lot of letters stuffed in his mail slot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.25,0:06:03.71,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Someone said he might be staying at another person's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.08,0:06:06.22,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.75,0:06:09.93,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,One of those letters may have been important.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.90,0:06:13.01,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder where he went.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.12,0:06:19.54,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you done yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.54,0:06:22.10,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Just put a little spit on cuts like these and they'll heal up fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.10,0:06:23.94,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,What'll you do if it gets infected?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.94,0:06:25.77,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, close your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.16,0:06:31.03,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.69,0:06:36.79,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Ri'ko, I'm glad you're in the same class as Richie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.87,0:06:42.04,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, would you look after him for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.55,0:06:48.36,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Um, well, I'd better get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.36,0:06:52.05,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Richie! Glad I caught up to \Nyou before you went home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.51,0:06:55.89,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Are those tears?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:06:59.81,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,This glob looks like a tear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.71,0:07:02.94,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,That's the tear of a broken heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.39,0:07:06.23,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,In Greek mythology, the god Apollo
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.23,0:07:09.42,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,fell in love with Daphne, \Nthe daughter of a river god.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.42,0:07:13.16,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,He became obsessed and chased her all around, but she wouldn't stop running.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.45,0:07:16.53,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,At last, she gave Apollo \Nthe ultimate rejection
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.53,0:07:19.00,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,by turning into a bay laurel tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.50,0:07:21.79,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,What an awful case of heartbreak!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.09,0:07:23.32,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Of course he would cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.32,0:07:27.09,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,He was so grief-stricken that he fashioned a wreath out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.84,0:07:28.80,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Who...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.80,0:07:29.59,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Who's he?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.77,0:07:33.72,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,This is Matsuoka Seiji, \Na second-year student.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:35.70,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,He's the great hope of East High's art club.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.70,0:07:39.15,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, stop it! You're embarrassing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.15,0:07:40.85,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Kawabuchi Sentaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.30,0:07:43.35,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,We're both in class 10, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.65,0:07:45.36,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.34,0:07:51.43,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Richie, do you remember that guy from last year?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.43,0:07:52.32,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.94,0:07:54.52,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gettin' the chills.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.52,0:07:56.53,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right, Sentaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.53,0:07:59.70,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Are you free on our next day off?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.08,0:08:02.62,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I want to get you a present as thanks for being my model.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.76,0:08:09.63,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait up! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.13,0:08:12.47,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! Apollo, my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.85,0:08:16.15,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I could never see this guy wearing a laurel wreath!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.47,0:08:28.23,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ri, do you have detention?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.78,0:08:32.66,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I forgot my math homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.66,0:08:35.22,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,That's unusual for someone as level-headed as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.41,0:08:39.91,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Who said I was level-headed? \NI'm careless as can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.22,0:08:43.41,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I get more absent-minded in the spring, but better snap out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.24,0:08:45.76,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,This song...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.76,0:08:48.15,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It's from "The Sound of Music".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.03,0:08:51.92,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I love this song.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.92,0:08:55.65,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I figured you would like that movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.65,0:08:58.46,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, I didn't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.46,0:09:00.78,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to, but before I knew it, it'd already stopped playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.52,0:09:03.40,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I bet it was a good movie, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.40,0:09:04.94,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,How could I miss it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.52,0:09:09.19,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I thought I'd be able to see it anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.82,0:09:11.62,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty dumb, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.25,0:09:27.08,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What is that again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.08,0:09:28.96,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,"My Favorite Things".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.96,0:09:30.46,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:50.81,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Better not. I had my shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.91,0:09:55.44,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, there was somethin' I wanted your advice about, Richie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.82,0:09:58.07,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,About... my date.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.93,0:10:00.89,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,With Yurika?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.89,0:10:02.05,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.08,0:10:07.77,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'll give the perfect advice for a romantic beginner like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:09.91,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.67,0:10:12.38,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:14.30,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.30,0:10:18.62,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,On a one-on-one date, you're sure to freeze up and blow the whole deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.62,0:10:20.48,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't make fun of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.48,0:10:22.64,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I can handle a date, piece of cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.07,0:10:26.03,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sure! You really think \Nyou can keep TPO in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.03,0:10:28.79,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,in front of that princess and behave accordingly?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.79,0:10:29.85,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,T-TP?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.85,0:10:32.62,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You know what it is? You don't, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.62,0:10:35.03,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,But for your own sake, you better not go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.10,0:10:37.27,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,TP...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.76,0:10:42.03,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Man, what a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.65,0:10:45.73,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I wish everyone would just stop falling in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.03,0:10:56.88,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot! Well, don't blame me for what happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.56,0:11:12.52,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sentaro, don't hold back. Tell me if you see something you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.89,0:11:18.15,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Oh, nah. I never get expensive stuff like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.15,0:11:21.28,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Even this jacket is a hand-me-down from Jun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.28,0:11:23.32,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.51,0:11:29.62,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,And from then on, he was all we talked about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.76,0:11:35.97,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Jun used to be the coolest kid in his high school!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.97,0:11:38.59,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,He was good at fightin', smart too...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:40.67,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.67,0:11:42.34,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,We had a good time talkin' about him,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:46.58,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,but now all I got left is a feelin' of emptiness in the pit of my stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.58,0:11:47.85,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Sen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.48,0:11:50.19,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Did your date go well?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.19,0:11:52.38,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,C-Course it did!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.38,0:11:56.86,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. A date is a piece of cake for you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.33,0:11:59.19,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.19,0:12:00.19,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.53,0:12:04.95,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't go well at all, did it? Just like I predicted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.51,0:12:09.20,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sen, stay away from her from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.87,0:12:12.87,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What makes you say that all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.88,0:12:18.44,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You really are dense, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.44,0:12:22.34,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Any way you look at it, you and a refined girl like that just don't match up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.03,0:12:25.10,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,She's out of your league.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.85,0:12:32.18,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Crap. I went too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.66,0:12:38.35,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Kawabuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.61,0:12:40.23,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.67,0:12:43.88,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you went on a date with Yurika?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.88,0:12:47.37,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,She said she had a great time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:50.24,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.24,0:12:52.41,apollon main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she say anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.41,0:12:53.63,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.89,0:12:59.00,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh! She said you were handsome
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.40,0:13:01.69,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,and that maybe she'll hold your hand next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.69,0:13:02.17,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.05,0:13:09.05,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're already here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.58,0:13:13.64,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you wanna try playin'\N"My Favorite Things" again together?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.35,0:13:18.56,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? I thought he'd be mad at me for what I said at lunch,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.20,0:13:21.23,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,but he seems to be in a great mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.90,0:13:26.00,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.87,0:13:29.28,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I thought only jazz was allowed in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.61,0:13:34.29,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that kid with the bowl cut, Matsuoka, forced it on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.92,0:13:37.52,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't refuse, so I just carried it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.80,0:13:41.30,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.24,0:13:46.30,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you, making a nice friend that lends you records.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.75,0:13:49.05,apollon main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.05,0:13:50.86,apollon main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Would you come upstairs a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.86,0:13:52.27,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.06,0:13:55.61,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What, did a new record come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.61,0:13:57.48,apollon main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Just come up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.48,0:13:58.06,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.17,0:14:02.57,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Is he going to listen to that record?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.26,0:14:07.50,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What am I so anxious about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.89,0:14:12.27,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Kawabuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.27,0:14:14.18,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Did you listen to the record I gave you yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.18,0:14:19.83,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I can't get into music that has girls squealin' over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.99,0:14:23.83,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that the purpose of making music?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.83,0:14:25.93,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you wanna become popular?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.93,0:14:27.46,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Don't really care about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.18,0:14:30.65,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'm not interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.65,0:14:32.51,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I wanna be popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.51,0:14:35.35,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,My dream is to become a star!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.82,0:14:37.60,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? A star?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.60,0:14:39.35,apollon main,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H272A70&\bord1\shad0\fs38\3c&H0B0C1E&\fnRaysHand\b0\pos(823,551)\frz10.586}Seiji
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.04,0:14:43.30,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second! Are those the underpants of somebody who's aiming to be a star?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.30,0:14:44.52,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, these?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.52,0:14:47.69,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a lot of brothers, so if I don't stake my claim like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.69,0:14:49.20,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,they'll disappear in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.63,0:14:53.15,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,And we're poor, so we can't afford to buy new ones often.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.15,0:14:57.14,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Amongst all my brothers, I'm called the "good-for-nothing".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.14,0:14:59.21,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Really, singing is the only thing I'm good at.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.72,0:15:04.96,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna prove that I can become somebody who's able to support his family.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.30,0:15:11.22,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,To me, this band is the first step. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.77,0:15:15.50,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Kawabuchi, I need your talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.29,0:15:35.58,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,A-Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.19,0:15:39.19,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,That was wonderful, Maruo! \NMuch better than I expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.19,0:15:40.37,apollon main,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.67,0:15:44.04,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,All right, now all we need is a drummer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.44,0:15:47.96,apollon main,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,Seiji, are you gonna tell me who it is you have in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.63,0:15:52.02,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you'll find out soon enough. \NBe ready for a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.49,0:15:55.60,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ri'ko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.90,0:15:56.92,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.92,0:16:00.10,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,School's out tomorrow, so if you're free,\Nwanna go to the beach?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.28,0:16:02.85,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Ma told me to take the munchkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.73,0:16:07.11,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,But lookin' after them alone is a tough job,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.50,0:16:10.12,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,so I thought I'd ask you along to help out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.61,0:16:14.01,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you're busy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.01,0:16:14.49,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.49,0:16:17.61,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on there. You free tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.53,0:16:20.55,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say we have us a \Nclammin' contest at the sea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.55,0:16:22.14,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? "Clamming"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.14,0:16:23.79,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Sentaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.11,0:16:26.57,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I like clamming, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.57,0:16:27.29,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ri...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.29,0:16:30.30,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What's "clamming"? Is it some kind of competition?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.15,0:16:37.82,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kaoru! Clamming means \Ndigging up clams at the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.81,0:16:40.81,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! It's confusing when this guy \Ncalls it a contest or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.38,0:16:42.57,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going too, Ri?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.50,0:16:44.33,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.33,0:16:45.27,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.76,0:16:48.90,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Then the threesome's set! \NThis is gonna be fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.02,0:16:53.27,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll need to mentally prepare myself this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.27,0:16:57.52,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,If those two have a romantic moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.52,0:17:02.14,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll casually get out of their way and just pray for Ri's happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.14,0:17:03.75,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,That was the idea,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.47,0:17:07.33,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,but maybe that's a non-issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.67,0:17:12.52,apollon main,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,I got a hamaguri clam!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.52,0:17:14.26,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,That's a short-necked clam.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.26,0:17:18.14,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Hi. Fancy meeting you here, Kawabuchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.14,0:17:19.97,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's a pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.27,0:17:23.08,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,What cute little girls and boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.08,0:17:25.24,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,You know, you can find a ton of razor clams over there
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.24,0:17:26.10,apollon main,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,Razors?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:28.74,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,You must be Ritsuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.74,0:17:30.60,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard about you from Yurika.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.60,0:17:33.35,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,She said you were exceptionally cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.61,0:17:36.82,apollon main,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Where are the razor clams?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.10,0:17:39.86,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, they're right over here. Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.66,0:17:44.25,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that guy? \NSweet-talking everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.25,0:17:46.65,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Don't criticize the guy when you don't know 'im.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.05,0:17:49.54,apollon main,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,Bro, you come too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.54,0:17:50.55,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.90,0:18:00.74,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty cool, right? Who wants to try it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.74,0:18:01.20,apollon main,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.20,0:18:02.27,apollon main,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Me, me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.27,0:18:02.89,apollon main,Taiichi,0000,0000,0000,,Salt!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.35,0:18:07.37,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they're having a good \Ntime over there. Shall we join them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.37,0:18:12.48,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pass. For some reason, that Matsuoka \Ncharacter rubs me the wrong way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.92,0:18:15.99,apollon main,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Taiichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.25,0:18:19.16,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! I'll be back in a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.41,0:18:23.37,apollon main,Taiichi,0000,0000,0000,,Crab!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.37,0:18:25.83,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,You were surprised when the \Ncrab pinched you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.25,0:18:27.76,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness that's all it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.92,0:18:36.92,apollon main,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Seiji! Don't tell me Kawabuchi's your drummer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.51,0:18:39.21,apollon main,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,Please, anybody but him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.21,0:18:41.53,apollon main,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm against it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.53,0:18:45.10,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't as scary as you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.56,0:18:49.56,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,All I have to do is set him free from what's tying him down,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.15,0:18:52.21,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,and then everything should work out the way I want it to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.62,0:18:56.10,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.82,0:18:58.46,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Catchin' any short-necks?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.69,0:19:01.63,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Better not underestimate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.63,0:19:03.78,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm good at this kind of simple task.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.40,0:19:06.37,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I ain't gonna lose either!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.37,0:19:07.29,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.29,0:19:09.10,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Clammin' contest!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.71,0:19:12.06,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What do I get if I win?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.06,0:19:14.46,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,How about the record that Ri's dad gave you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.46,0:19:17.13,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about it! 'Cause I'm gonna win anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:18.80,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,What about the Beatles record?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.87,0:19:24.00,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Kawabuchi, did you listen to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.85,0:19:28.56,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I heard it. Wasn't bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.26,0:19:30.90,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Did it stir up your interest?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.90,0:19:33.65,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't go that far. But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.69,0:19:37.50,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinkin' I'll help you out with
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.50,0:19:38.99,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,that band you're gonna have \Nfor the school festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.99,0:19:40.19,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.19,0:19:42.26,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,You'll join my rock band?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.26,0:19:42.87,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.87,0:19:43.78,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.74,0:19:46.90,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Richie, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.15,0:19:46.90,apollon main,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.90,0:19:50.00,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just gonna be away 'til the festival's over with.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.71,0:19:53.29,apollon main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,We'll only be apart for a while, Nishimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:55.17,apollon main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Let's send each other letters, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.67,0:19:59.59,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Fuck you! {orig: in a pig's ass! - dunno wtf...}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.77,0:20:02.47,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I was wrong about you, traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.79,0:20:08.90,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Richie, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.90,0:20:10.02,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.02,0:20:11.15,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.15,0:20:12.48,apollon main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to listen to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.75,0:20:16.94,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.97,0:20:22.53,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.82,0:20:24.00,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.09,0:20:34.50,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I know. I acted like an angry little kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.19,0:20:40.00,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,But being separated from him scares the hell out of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.97,0:20:43.51,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I abandoned him without thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.90,0:20:50.17,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Since coming here, I'd forgotten
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.17,0:20:52.39,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,that I'm not good at getting along with other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.70,0:20:54.97,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It's better this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.63,0:20:58.73,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I've made it this far all on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.10,0:21:02.89,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,No problem... at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.77,0:21:09.91,apollon main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.91,0:21:11.93,apollon main,Bartender,0000,0000,0000,,Tsutomu, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.89,0:21:14.41,apollon main,Bartender,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the end of the counter!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.60,0:21:19.67,apollon main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be.
